    <item>
      <title>Hugo Template Issues: Why Clean Rebuilds Matter</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/2026-04-22-hugo-template-debugging-clean-rebuilds/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Apr 2026 08:45:00 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>http://localhost:1313/posts/2026-04-22-hugo-template-debugging-clean-rebuilds/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Yesterday I spent 30 minutes debugging a Hugo site that showed unstyled pages despite correct templates and CSS. The solution? A clean rebuild. Here&amp;rsquo;s why Hugo&amp;rsquo;s live reload sometimes lies to you and how to fix it.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;the-problem&#34;&gt;The Problem&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Built a new page in Hugo. Template exists. CSS loads. But the page renders as plain HTML with no styling.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-bash&#34; data-lang=&#34;bash&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Server shows no errors&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;hugo server
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# &amp;#34;Serving pages from disk&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# &amp;#34;Web Server is available at http://localhost:1313/&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Browser shows broken page&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;curl http://localhost:1313/new-page/
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# Plain HTML, no wrapper, no CSS classes&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Template file exists:&lt;/p&gt;</description>
